{"type":"message","id":"7b365071","parentId":"b7460751","timestamp":"2026-06-01T00:55:09.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending a new message \"新建接入Bot7\". Let me process this according to my workflow.\n\nFirst, I need to identify the user. The sender_id is \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\". Let me check if I have a User.md for this person.\n\nLet me also read my state files since this seems to be a new session.\n\nWait, the message seems to be about \"新建接入Bot7\" — they want to set up/register a new bot connection called \"Bot7\". Let me first check who this is.\n\nLet me follow my Step 0: identify user + load state.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HsChsZx0sqxB6HqchSqr4999","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md 2>&1"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md 2>&1\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":297,"output":223,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":140,"totalTokens":20872,"cost":{"input":0.000041580000000000005,"output":0.00006244,"cacheRead":0.000569856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000673876}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780275307326,"responseId":"a7e9d3bc-bc71-4e6e-a5dc-d50e544a711b"}}
