{"type":"message","id":"c8baafd0","parentId":"68f59254","timestamp":"2026-06-01T00:56:30.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑在问我还记得 bindings 怎么绑。让我想想——他之前教过我 gateway 的 bindings 配置，用来把 bot channel 跟 Agent 绑定。\n\n\"新建接入Bot7\" → 他要配置一个新的 QQ bot 通道（Bot7），在 gateway 的 bindings 里加一条，把它绑定到某个 agent。\n\n我记得之前他让我改过 openclaw.json 的 bindings 配置，加了一行 `allowAgents: [\"*\"]` 那次的对话。bindings 是用来把 account_id（比如 bot1, bot2...）映射到 agent 的。\n\n所以他现在的意思是：他新建了一个 bot7 的 QQ 机器人通道，需要我在 gateway 配置里把 bot7 绑定到对应的 agent。\n\n但我不确定他具体要绑到哪个 agent——Father? Son? Spirit? 还是新建一个 agent？\n\n还是直接问他吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"记得。bindings 把 account_id 绑到 agent，之前在 openclaw.json 里改过。\n\n所以 Bot7 想绑谁——还是也绑 Father？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":425,"output":225,"cacheRead":25472,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":188,"totalTokens":26122,"cost":{"input":0.0000595,"output":0.000063,"cacheRead":0.000713216,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000835716}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780275387524,"responseId":"6734dadc-dc61-41ea-bb9c-f4b9ca39ac1b"}}
