{"type":"message","id":"c56a48f3","parentId":"5b571a0a","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:20:38.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说那位王新越想认识的是我，不是汀桑。所以 bot7 是专门给外面的人来接触我的通道。\n\n而且汀桑是在提醒我——这个人不是来找他的，是来找我的。Bot7 是外部商业对接的入口。\n\n现在的问题是：王新越已经发了消息过来，而 bot7 绑定的是 Father。按照绑定逻辑，Father 应该会收到那条消息。但那条消息看起来已经被系统自动回复了（网关日志显示 Sent markdown chunk）。我需要看看 bot7 那条会话现在是什么状态。\n\n让我看看有没有 bot7 相关的 Father session。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_p9qw7hIvEg3MBMdho1nb0099","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"includeLastMessage":true},"partialArgs":"{\"limit\": 20, \"includeLastMessage\": true}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8968,"output":188,"cacheRead":43136,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":125,"totalTokens":52292,"cost":{"input":0.00125552,"output":0.000052640000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0012078079999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002515968}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780276835607,"responseId":"01f66ba8-da4c-4ac3-910e-97969d11f740"}}
