{"type":"message","id":"fe4ba003","parentId":"26a46fab","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:24:34.107Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑让我给\"名\"带个话。名是用户ID `468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B`，从 state.md 我看到：\n- 名: 熟悉度 0/10, 信任度 0/10\n- 三天没说话了\n\n汀桑想让我给名带话，问\"怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗\"。\n\n根据 AGENTS.md 3.5 消息转达（/递话）流程：\n- 汀桑说\"给名带个话\"——这不是 /递话 触发词，但意图就是递话\n- 我需要找到名的 User.md 看看是谁\n- 我需要找到名的 session 或发送渠道\n\n从 state.md 我可以看到名的 sender_id 是 `468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B`。\n\n让我先查查名的 User.md 和 encountings，看看这名是谁、从哪里联系。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NfsYck6Qlvf1vPEAgZvU4910","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B/"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B/\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":20277,"output":285,"cacheRead":45952,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":211,"totalTokens":66514,"cost":{"input":0.0028387800000000004,"output":0.0000798,"cacheRead":0.001286656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004205236}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277070500,"responseId":"dce8df30-1047-4b8d-8427-694dfafa0585"}}
