{"type":"message","id":"4230b216","parentId":"f4e6e3e8","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:26:44.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see two things:\n\n1. Bot2 is having Error 4009 (session timed out) repeatedly - this means bot2's WebSocket connection to QQ's API keeps timing out. So even if the agent completes, the bot2 channel can't send messages because the WebSocket session keeps expiring.\n\n2. There was another attempt to create a cron with systemEvent to main session, but it was restricted.\n\nThe root issue is that bot2 has persistent websocket timeouts (Error 4009). This isn't something I can fix from here - it's a QQ API connectivity issue.\n\nLet me tell 汀桑 the situation - bot2 的 WebSocket 一直在超时，消息发不过去。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"查到了。Bot2 的 WebSocket 一直在报 Error 4009（session timed out），消息发不过去——不是我的问题，是 bot2 跟 QQ 那边的连接断了。\n\n你是不是得重启一下 bot2 的凭证或者检查一下 token？不然名那边的消息到不了😓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3869,"output":210,"cacheRead":72704,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":146,"totalTokens":76783,"cost":{"input":0.00054166,"output":0.000058800000000000006,"cacheRead":0.002035712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002636172}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780277201137,"responseId":"527a0acd-4993-48b5-8181-afbe1b8ac9f6"}}
