{"type":"message","id":"088f31fe","parentId":"aad7389b","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:27:26.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No \"Sent\" entries for bot2, which means the message was not actually sent. The 200 OK at 09:26:16 was probably a different API call (token refresh, etc.), not a message send.\n\nSo the cron job is failing for a different reason. Let me think about what approach will work.\n\nSince bot2 WebSocket is connected and API calls are returning 200 OK, the channel should be functional. The issue might be with how I'm creating the cron job.\n\nLet me try a simpler approach - create a cron job with just the bare minimum to announce a text message to bot2.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FUhdGnTHs3e6Udew2tPw4535","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"递话 名","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-06-01T01:28:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"你给汀桑传句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot2","to":"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B"},"deleteAfterRun":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"递话 名\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-06-01T01:28:00Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"你给汀桑传句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"accountId\":\"bot2\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":89,"output":299,"cacheRead":82816,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":126,"totalTokens":83204,"cost":{"input":0.000012460000000000001,"output":0.00008372,"cacheRead":0.002318848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002415028}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277243609,"responseId":"b304f028-2ead-4236-b602-3a02756d6562"}}
