{"type":"message","id":"e8451dd7","parentId":"7a7507d1","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:28:40.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same issue - the cron job is failing. The error \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话推送-汀桑-名 failed\" seems to be a generic cron failure message. The isolated session is created but the agentTurn fails.\n\nThe issue might be that the isolated session for an agentTurn is failing for some reason - maybe the model is not configured for isolated sessions or there's a context issue.\n\nLet me try a different approach. Instead of using an isolated agentTurn, let me try a systemEvent delivered via announce mode. But systemEvent needs sessionTarget=\"main\"... \n\nActually, let me revisit the design. The cron tool description says:\n- isolated agentTurn defaults to announce\n- The delivery is supposed to announce the agent's output\n\nBut maybe the issue is that the isolated session agent has trouble. Let me try a different approach - use the direct sessions_send with a different session key format. \n\nActually, let me try something else. Maybe I should just send the message by replying to the user in my current session and letting the channel routing handle it. But no, 汀桑 wants me to send to 名 via bot2 channel.\n\nLet me try sending via an exec command or through sessions_send to a specific session key. Actually, I think the session key format for bot2's session with user 名 might be different. Let me check what sessions exist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这 crontab 递话一直失败💦 我换个方式试试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lly5gVolIqkBJcqSqOPO2817","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"remove","jobId":"e9f145b7-367e-486d-9598-df5f8452659f"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"remove\", \"jobId\": \"e9f145b7-367e-486d-9598-df5f8452659f\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":663,"output":385,"cacheRead":91520,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":286,"tot