{"type":"message","id":"58e5b473","parentId":"cec0b89d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:49.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! I found the key log:\n\n```\n[bot2] WebSocket closed: 4009 Session timed out\n```\n\nBot2 keeps timing out. The WebSocket disconnect happens every ~30 minutes. And when I try to send a message via bot2 through the cron job, the isolated session spawns Son, but at 09:29:06 there was:\n```\nSubagent announce give up (retry-limit)... deliveryError=\"announce deferred or direct delivery failed\"\n```\n\nSo the announce delivery to bot2 failed because bot2's WebSocket was timing out right at that moment.\n\nThe issue is bot2's connection instability. Let me just tell 汀桑 that bot2 is having persistent WebSocket timeouts, which is why the message couldn't go through. It's a QQ platform issue - the session keeps expiring.\n\nLet me check the current job bb92bbc6 status.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_O4XBswC6EcKokkynVoDo5074","name":"cron","arguments":{"jobId":"bb92bbc6-da47-4398-abc7-69666c1c4362","action":"get"},"partialArgs":"{\"jobId\": \"bb92bbc6-da47-4398-abc7-69666c1c4362\", \"action\": \"get\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5898,"output":264,"cacheRead":111104,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":184,"totalTokens":117266,"cost":{"input":0.0008257200000000001,"output":0.00007392000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003110912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004010552}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277446750,"responseId":"eed9558f-432e-4d2d-bd22-082b7c981bd5"}}
