{"type":"message","id":"2f45b796","parentId":"695ff3f0","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:31:00.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the job ran for 52 seconds and still failed with `lastDelivered: false, lastDeliveryStatus: \"not-delivered\"`. The lastFailureNotification was delivered to me (the main session), which is probably what 汀桑 saw.\n\nThe root cause is clear: bot2 has persistent WebSocket timeout issues (Error 4009). The cron job can spawn the isolated session and the agentTurn runs fine, but when it tries to announce/deliver the message via bot2's channel, the delivery fails because bot2's WebSocket connection to QQ's server keeps timing out.\n\nSo the issue isn't really on my end, it's a bot2 connectivity issue. Let me inform 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Bot2 的 WebSocket 连 QQ 一直超时（Error 4009），30 分钟断一次。消息发不出去了——不是我这边的问题，是 bot2 跟 QQ 开放平台的会话不稳定。\n\n你看看 bot2 的 clientSecret 是不是过期了？Token 能拿下来，但 WebSocket 连上就断😓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":637,"output":222,"cacheRead":117760,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":147,"totalTokens":118619,"cost":{"input":0.00008918000000000001,"output":0.00006216,"cacheRead":0.00329728,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034486200000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780277457728,"responseId":"67875381-49aa-460a-926b-956e33f52976"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5534eaa4","parentId":"2f45b796","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:31:17.533Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"bot2是通的吧，没通我给你检查一下clientSecret","timestamp":1780277462752}}
{"type":"message","id":"aca202b3","parentId":"5534eaa4","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:31:22.239Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑说bot2应该是通的，让我检查一下clientSecret。他说\"bot2是通的吧，没通我给你检查一下clientSecret\"——意思是bot2应该是正常的，如果真不通他就去检查clientSecret。\n\n让我再确认一下bot2的真实状态。从日志看，bot2确实能连接上WebSocket，但每隔约30分钟就会断一次（Error 4009）。不过它也会自动重新连接。\n\n但刚才的递话失败可能是因为在递话发送的那一刻，bot2刚好处在超时重连的窗口期。\n\n让我再检查一下最新的bot2状态日志。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_AgZjroH1HqHxv1ukcCAy0049","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -E \"bot2.*WebSocket|bot2.*Access token|bot2.*Gateway ready|bot2.*Error\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-06-01.log | tail -15"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -E \\\"bot2.*WebSocket|bot2.*Access token|bot2.*Gateway ready|bot2.*Error\\\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-06-01.log | tail -15\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":48107,"output":215,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":125,"totalTokens":118850,"cost":{"input":0.006734980000000001,"output":0.000060200000000000006,"cacheRead":0.001974784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008769964}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277478104,"responseId":"95d90767-83b0-4e56-a888-34c68fcc41db"}}
