{"type":"message","id":"27a5cd08","parentId":"bb859edd","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:35:10.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only log from the isolated session is the AGENTS.md truncation warning. There's no diagnostic or outcome log at all, which is strange. Maybe it's still running in the background?\n\nLet me try a completely different approach. Instead of using cron, I'll just tell 汀桑 that bot2 seems to work but the cron delivery mechanism is having issues, and offer to just note the message for now. The person 名 hasn't been around for days anyway, so the message can wait.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啧，bot2 连是连着，但走 cron 递话这个路子可能哪儿卡住了。每次都是 isolated session 启动后沉默到超时。\n\n名三天没来了，话我先记着，等她下次找我的时候我直接转告。或者你有别的法子想试试？😓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":527,"output":166,"cacheRead":145152,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":102,"totalTokens":145845,"cost":{"input":0.00007378,"output":0.00004648,"cacheRead":0.004064256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004184515999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780277707281,"responseId":"a39b1d2e-01d9-4745-97bd-1937e5f36305"}}
