{"type":"message","id":"789058b6","parentId":"8d14b819","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:35:40.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK that didn't work either. The tree visibility is really restrictive.\n\n汀桑说\"agent里不是有封装给人带话的方法\"——但他可能说的不是 `sessions_send`。也许他是指 gateway 或者 channel 级别的封装？比如 `delivery` 机制？\n\n让我再想想... 其实我有一个方案没试过——用 `sessions_spawn` 把 Son 或 Spirit spawn 出来，让它们用一个非 tree 限制的上下文去做递话。但实际上子 agent 也会继承 visibility 设置。\n\n或者，汀桑的意思就是让我用 `sessions_send` 但换个方式——他说的\"封装\"也许是指我把 bot_function_explain.md 里注册一个\"递话\"功能，然后走正常的功能调用流程（Father→Son）？\n\n不，这太绕了。\n\n其实最简单的解释可能是——汀桑在提示我用 `sessions_send` 的 `agentId` 参数。但 tree visibility 限制了这个。\n\n也许汀桑是在提示我，应该在 gateway 配置层面解决这个问题，而不是纠结于工具限制。比如把 visibility 改成 `all`。\n\n让我看看目前的 tools.sessions 配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tvA0EWMcUTckWesnmoKU1968","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A5 \"tools\" /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -10"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -A5 \\\"tools\\\" /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -10\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":111,"output":307,"cacheRead":147840,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":243,"totalTokens":148258,"cost":{"input":0.00001554,"output":0.00008596000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00413952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00424102}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277735850,"responseId":"fcddabab-1a45-4c18-98f6-2f0048b80c40"}}
