{"type":"message","id":"5bffedbf","parentId":"24e5982d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:35:57.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Son's functions don't have a message passing/delivery function. So Son won't have a \"轮子\" for delivering messages to other users.\n\n汀桑说的\"封装\"可能不是指 Son 的功能。让我想想...\n\n也许他说的\"封装\"是 gateway/channel 层面的。在 OpenClaw 里，每个 channel 应该都可以直接发送消息。但作为 agent，我跨 session 发送的能力被 tree visibility 限制了。\n\n实际上，我现在能想到的最后一个方案是——用 `delivery` 机制直接发。cron 的 announce 模式就是这个机制。只不过我之前用 cron+isolated agentTurn 的方式每次都失败了。\n\n让我试试直接用 cron 的 announce 模式，但不经过 isolated agentTurn——直接把消息作为 announce 发出去。但是 cron 的 payload 只能是 agentTurn 或 systemEvent...\n\n让我想想——也许汀桑暗示的是另一个我没注意到的工具？或者 gateway 层面的命令？\n\n其实，汀桑可能是提示我查 docs，看看 OpenClaw 里有没有原生的消息传递封装。让我查查文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_naPnpvHiowzKNFv9Vis34291","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rl \"delivery\\|announce\\|message.*send\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ 2>/dev/null | head -10"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -rl \\\"delivery\\\\|announce\\\\|message.*send\\\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ 2>/dev/null | head -10\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":111,"output":299,"cacheRead":148992,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":222,"totalTokens":149402,"cost":{"input":0.00001554,"output":0.00008372,"cacheRead":0.004171776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004271036000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277752724,"responseId":"2e9d3310-0fcc-4290-829e-7f6ca1f34ded"}}
