{"type":"message","id":"cb2f166b","parentId":"2c09bc81","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:14:23.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! In AGENTS.md, section 3.6 already defines the 递话 (message delivery) flow! It's a `/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>` trigger that handles the entire process.\n\nThe key part is at line 303-311:\n```\n名称: deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\n...\nmessage: \"{from_name}托我带话：{内容}\",\n...\ndelivery: {\n  mode: \"announce\",\n  channel: \"qqbot\",\n  accountId: \"{bot_channel}\",\n  to: \"qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\"\n}\n```\n\nSo the flow is:\n1. User says `/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>` or expresses the intent\n2. I look up the user by their 称呼 in the state.md relationship table\n3. Find their bot_channel\n4. Create a cron job with announce delivery to deliver the message\n\nBut I didn't go through this flow correctly! 汀桑 didn't say \"/递话 名 怎么起这么早...\" — he just said \"给名带个话\". And instead of properly looking up the delivery info and formatting the message correctly, I tried a bunch of ad-hoc methods that didn't work.\n\nAnd the key difference: the AGENTS.md says to use a very specific cron job format. Let me re-read the exact template and follow it properly.\n\nFrom AGENTS.md around line 300-321:\n\n```\n#### 存话 + 递话流程\n\n触发: 用户说 \"/递话 <对方称呼> <内容>\" 或明确表达让带话的意图\n\nStep 1: 确认 + 找 sender\n  → 根据\"对方称呼\"在 state.md 关系温度表查找匹配的用户\n  → 找到 → 继续\n  → 没找到 → 回复用户：\"我不认识叫这个的人\"\n\nStep 2: 存话记录（创建一次性 cron）\n  → 取该用户的 bot_channel + sender_id\n  → 创建一次性 cron：\n      name: \"deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\"\n      schedule: { kind:\"at\", at: now+3s }\n      sessionTarget: \"isolated\"\n      payload: {\n        kind: \"agentTurn\",\n        message: \"{from_name}托我带话：{content}\",\n      }\n      delivery: {\n        mode: \"announce\",\n        channel: \"qqbot\",\n        accountId: \"{bot_channel}\",\n        to: \"qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\"\n      }\n      deleteAfterRun: true\n\nStep 3: 告知用户\n  → 回复：\"话已存，等{对方称呼}上线我会转告\"\n  → 等待短暂后，查 cron.get(jobId) 看 delivery 状态\n  → 如果 delivery 失败：回应用户 \"推送好像没成功，{对方称呼}的bot好像离线了，他上线我再转告\"\n  → 如果成功：回应用户 \"好了，话带到了\"\n```\n\nThe template is very specific. Let me follow it exactly this time. The key things I was doing wrong:\n1. The message format should be `\"{from_name}托我带话：{content}\"`\n2. The name format should be \"deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\"\n\nLet me do it properly this time.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"汀桑你确实写过😓 在 AGENTS.md 的 3.6 节——`/递话` 流程，一次性 cron + announce delivery，格式都定好了。我光顾着自己折腾，没按流程走。\n\n重来，按你写的规矩来。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aUsjvoaaMOYaOcNX7DdN7152","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"deliver-汀桑-名","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-06-01T01:35:00Z"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"汀桑托我带话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot2","to":"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B"},"deleteAfterRun":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"deliver-汀桑-名\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-06-01T01:35:00Z\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"汀桑托我带话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\",\"timeoutSeconds\":120},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"accountId\":\"bot2\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1538,"output":952,"cacheRead":152960,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":706,"totalTokens":155450,"cost":{"input":0.00021532000000000002,"output":0.00026656,"cacheRead":0.00428288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00476476}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780280056179,"responseId":"de3f6018-f22b-4a4e-a4c2-4704b211d942"}}
