\":\"file:///usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"179\",\"filePath\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179\",\"method\":\"logToFile\"}},\"time\":\"2026-06-01T10:15:01.686+08:00\",\"hostname\":\"iZwz9fsb7hxrqc27t9an22Z\",\"message\":\"workspace bootstrap file AGENTS.md is 13968 chars (limit 12000); truncating in injected context (sessionKey=agent:father:cron:1aa41a2a-436e-46c2-930c-7f3d907c94c7:run:2286e4c0-f156-4383-84bc-462a6fd108d0)\",\"traceId\":\"3c90ff7795978f6fd35bc4c8b39fd7dd\",\"spanId\":\"9706eac6d0f639c0\",\"traceFlags\":\"01\"}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8896,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780280145052}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba6930aa","parentId":"155f5982","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:15:49.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at this all more carefully, I notice something important: the first \"deliver-汀桑-名\" job I created had the wrong time (past time) and got rejected. Then I created 1aa41a2a with the correct time 02:15:00Z.\n\nBut I don't see any diagnostic/outcome log for 1aa41a2a. It ran for about 35 seconds (10:15:01 to 10:15:36). No \"Sent\" for bot2. No diagnostic error log.\n\nWait - maybe the issue is that in my most recent job (1aa41a2a), I was writing to the same cron file from a different tool session context, and the jobs were overlapping and failing.\n\nActually, I think the issue might be simpler. Looking at the error for previous cron jobs:\n\n`Subagent announce give up (retry-limit)... deliveryError=\"announce deferred or direct delivery failed\"`\n\nThis means the isolated agentTurn spawned *Son* (a subagent) to process the message, and then tried to announce Son's output to the delivery target. But the announce failed because... the Son subagent's output couldn't be announced.\n\nBut for 1aa41a2a - there's NO error log at all. The job ran, completed (deleted), but there's no record of what happened. Maybe it completed successfully and the delivery went through?\n\nLet me check the bot2 channel logs between 10:15:00 and 10:16:00 more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_OxpLMQ55NwOaUVuOkokg7795","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep \"bot2\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-06-01.log | grep \"10:15\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep \\\"bot2\\\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-06-01.log | grep \\\"10:15\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3065,"output":392,"cacheRead":170368,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":321,"totalTokens":173825,"cost":{"input":0.0004291,"output":0.00010976,"cac