{"type":"message","id":"ea758cdd","parentId":"0fcf4deb","timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:16:28.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've added the row. Now let me also update the note at the top to clarify that not all triggered functions go to Son — some like `/递话` are handled by Father directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了。加了 `/递话`、`递话`、`给*带个话`、`给*带句话`、`帮我给*说` 这些触发词，处理路径标的是 → Father。\n\n下次谁再说\"给名带句话\"或者 `/递话 名 xxx`，我就自动走 3.6 流程了😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":142,"output":119,"cacheRead":178176,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":41,"totalTokens":178437,"cost":{"input":0.000019880000000000003,"output":0.00003332,"cacheRead":0.004988928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005042128}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780280186604,"responseId":"2d87c526-36cd-4afb-8b02-45dc306b0401"}}
